headline: Pacific Biosciences of California (PACB) Reports Q1 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Pacific Biosciences (PACB) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 21.05% and 6.15%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: STERIS (NYSE:STE) Announces Quarterly Dividend of US$0.57 Per Share
summary: STERIS (NYSE:STE) recently affirmed its commitment to shareholder value with the announcement of a quarterly interim dividend of $0.57 per share, set for payment in late June 2025. Over the last month, the company’s share price rose 6%, potentially bolstered by this dividend affirmation, underscoring its financial stability. This moves comes amidst wider market optimism spurred by news of a trade deal between the U.S. and U.K. The general market rise did see major indices like the Dow and S&P...
